divs: Sighting DetailsI was by myself watching TV. Suddenly did I felt like I should give birth. I wasn't pregnant but I felt anyway I should give birth. I lay me down at the floor with pillows behind my knees. But I started to bleeding so much so I had to go and standing in the bath-tub. I had no cramp or pain. And out from me come two after birth plasmas ! They were grey purple and big as a mans hands so I think it was 9 month birth plasma. I lay it in a plastic bag with water and when my husband come home in the morning I said that he had to take me to the hospital. The Doctor checked me out and said he couldn't see I have been pregnant and thought it was menstruation bleeding. In his office did I gave him the plastic bag and asked him if I haven't given birth. He was shocked and send it to research but I never heard back from them again.
